Terraform function:
The terraform language includes a number of built in factors that you can use to terraform and combine values.
The general syantax for function callls is a function is a function name followed by comma separated arguments in parathesis:

function (arguments1,arguments2)
Example:
> max(5,12,9) 12


** Terraform Function**  (Search google on terraform function)

The terraform lanaguage doesnot support user-defined functions and so only the functions build into the lanaguage available for use:

Numeric 
string



lookup is afunction

lookup(map,key,default)

example:
lookup({a="ay",b="bee"},"a","what?")
output >> ay

lookup({a="ay",b="bee"},"c","what?")
output >> what?

If We want to trouble of terraform plan
check issue 

export TF_LOG=Trace

then terraform plan


to save log of terraform log

export TF_LOG_PATH=/tmp/terraformlog



